WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
One bright fish swimming by

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Two sea stars on the sand

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Three coral branches reaching high

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Four crabs with claws so grand!

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Count with us in the reef today

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Maths and science all the way!